            <h1>Final Project Proposal</h1>
            
            <h2>Introduction</h2>
            
            <p>Mystical Magical Donuts </p>
            
            <p>Mystical Magical Donuts is a luxury donut shop devoted to creating the funkiest, most imaginative flavor combinations you won't find anywhere else. Every donut is made 100% from scratch daily, hand-cut, fried to perfection, and artfully decorated by some of the finest pastry artists in the city. Based in Long Beach, California, Mystical Magical Donuts is a locally owned, women-led business that uses only the highest-quality ingredients to invent bold, unforgettable creations.</p>
            
            <h2>Target Audience</h2>
            
            <p>Mystical Magical Donuts caters to a trendsetter/food enthusiast based audience. The brand attracts customers seeking a memorable food experience through its selection of unique, photogenic dessert concepts.</p>
           
            <p>Event planners, local community supporters, influencers, or just foodies in general will visit this site to browse current flavor collections, place online orders, request custom or event catering, learn about the brand story and values, or check store hours, location, and updates.</p>
            
